.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, subway, airplane
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, chess, mah-jongg
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the airplane is between the person playing whist and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Transport   | snowmobile        | subway | airplane  | tram |
| Game      | chess | monopoly  | mah-jongg | whist    |

