.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, mystery, spy
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, go, whist
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person playing go##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching musical movies is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching musical movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | mystery           | time-travel | spy  |
| Game         | canasta | whist | domino   | go |

