.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, blood-red, blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, rowing, biathlon, rugby
1. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who likes azure is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who likes blood-red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | blue   | light-blue | azure | blood-red      |
| Sport     | biathlon | surfing    | rowing  | rugby |

