.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, guinea-pig, horse
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing snooker is the owner of the snake##1
2. the person playing whist is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person playing backgammon##2
3. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Pet       | ferret | horse | guinea-pig     | snake   |
| Game   | backgammon   | whist     | chess | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, old-henry, fonseca, prince
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, chinese, american, polish
1. the fonseca-smoker is between the japanese and the vegafina-smoker##2
2. the polish is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the japanese is on the left of the polish##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | old-henry | fonseca | vegafina | prince |
| Nationality   | japanese         | polish       | chinese    | american         |

