.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, zinnia, tulip, begonia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, ritmeester, bluemaster, blend
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is between the person who growszinnia and the blend-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Flower    | begonia   | tulip      | zinnia   | aconite  |
| Cigar   | blend | ritmeester | bluemaster | davidoff |

