.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, dog, hedgehog
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the horse##2
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Pet          | horse     | chinchilla | hedgehog   | dog        |
| Game   | whist | canasta   | backgammon | mah-jongg |

