.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend, aristoff, pall-mall
1. the aristoff-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking sprite is the blend-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the blend-smoker is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | sprite | almond-milk | water |
| Cigar   | aristoff          | blend     | pall-mall  | old-henry     |

