.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
House: tower, cape-cod, modern, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the townhouse house is between the person drinking mirinda and the tower house##2
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| House         | tower      | townhouse | cape-cod  | modern |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk  | mirinda | lemonade    |

