.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, february, april
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, cooking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's birthday is in june##2
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | january | june | february | april |
| Hobby     | collecting     | skydiving   | photography | cooking  |

