.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, parkour, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, december, november, october
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | water-polo | lacrosse | golf | parkour |
| Birthday           | november  | october  | december | july      |

