.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, snooker, backgammon
There 4 different types of food: onion, watermelon, asparagus, orange
1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
3. the person playing whist is between the person eating onion and the person playing snooker##2
4. the person playing backgammon is the person eating onion##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Game       | backgammon | whist | snooker | canasta |
| Food   | onion    | watermelon  | orange    | asparagus       |

