The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, trance, rock
1. the fan funk is on the left of the fan rock##1
2. the fan folk is on the left of the fan funk##1
3. the person who likes blue is the fan folk##1
4. the fan rock is between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes aquamarine##2
5. the person who likes aquamarine is the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | blue   | apricot   | emerald | aquamarine |
| Music-Genre         | folk | funk | rock     | trance    |

