.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, coffee, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, jazz, rock
1. the fan reggae is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fan hip-hop and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | coffee    | mirinda     | soy-milk | water |
| Music-Genre     | reggae | rock | jazz       | hip-hop     |

 